<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_69D76107-0382-B4A5-78C1-5B256236EB16">Senate Majority Leader Chuck Schumer announced Thursday morning that a deal had been reached, paving the way for the final vote later in the day. An aide familiar with negotiations told CNN that the deal is to increase the ceiling by 
