<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_5A2E8759-F715-024A-46B2-5B40D7FC6774">Both parties have made clear that the country must not default and that even coming close to it would likely bring catastrophic economic consequences. 
<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_D58E4F84-4A28-8DF0-C879-5B3EA71861DD">Yet while the debt limit extension stands to avert immediate economic disaster, it does not resolve the underlying partisan stalemate over the issue. It merely delays the fight until another day. 
