<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_635668BE-EAB2-6DD8-8E57-5D45623CC543"><h3>Battle lines drawn</h3>
<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_107051EA-C81D-804B-EDDF-5B447E6EF09B">In a sign that partisan battle lines remain clearly drawn, McConnell said on Thursday that the agreement provides Democrats with more time to use reconciliation to raise the debt limit themselves. 
