<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_BDAEF357-E499-346F-99D8-5B32B7A406DC">Treasury Secretary Janet Yellen had warned lawmakers that the federal government will likely run out of cash by October 18 unless Congress raises the debt ceiling. 
<div class="zn-body__paragraph" data-paragraph-id="paragraph_0BEE8DD2-99FF-EDCD-5A62-5B36F658DF75">But Congress may not even have that long, since the deadline is more of a best guess estimate than a set in stone deadline. That dynamic intensified pressure on both sides to reach a deal this week. 
